{"ok":true,"page":1,"totalPages":22,"totalResults":433,"platform":"SonyLIV","type":"tv","items":[{"tmdbId":90966,"type":"tv","title":"Gullak","year":"2019","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/arn3mvRYSrEqO7vaKbH8QxM8EEK.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/t0J74zw5N5Ux7CvvBtIHvjnSB4n.jpg","rating":7.8,"overview":"Set in quaint by-lanes in the heart of India, Gullak is a collection of disarming and relatable tales of the Mishra family.","popularity":112.7846},{"tmdbId":95479,"type":"tv","title":"JUJUTSU KAISEN","year":"2020","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/fHpKWq9ayzSk8nSwqRuaAUemRKh.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/qpin8cASXEVtwhzNsprHYFiOAGk.jpg","rating":8.574,"overview":"Yuji Itadori is a boy with tremendous physical strength, though he lives a completely ordinary high school life. One day, to save a classmate who has been attacked by curses, he eats the finger of Ryomen Sukuna, taking the curse into his own soul. From then on, he shares one body with Ryomen Sukuna. Guided by the most powerful of sorcerers, Satoru Gojo, Itadori is admitted to Tokyo Jujutsu High School, an organization that fights the curses... and thus begins the heroic tale of a boy who became a curse to exorcise a curse, a life from which he could never turn back.","popularity":103.5888},{"tmdbId":65942,"type":"tv","title":"Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World-","year":"2016","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/5MrRCj7z92YLWMXHeWKp19eJPYv.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/x6y59dJBE1o0r4YRsWVQXE2nnlB.jpg","rating":7.9,"overview":"Natsuki Subaru, an ordinary high school  student, is on his way home from the convenience store when he finds  himself transported to another world. As he's lost and confused in a new  world where he doesn't even know left from right, the only person to  reach out to him was a beautiful girl with silver hair. Determined to  repay her somehow for saving him from his own despair, Subaru agrees to  help the girl find something she's looking for.","popularity":105.8441},{"tmdbId":71712,"type":"tv","title":"The Good Doctor","year":"2017","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/luhKkdD80qe62fwop6sdrXK9jUT.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/f3cin9kOz4nOrlYEMxGFQhv4bdN.jpg","rating":8.5,"overview":"Shaun Murphy, a young surgeon with autism and savant syndrome, relocates from a quiet country life to join a prestigious hospital's surgical unit. Unable to personally connect with those around him, Shaun uses his extraordinary medical gifts to save lives and challenge the skepticism of his colleagues.","popularity":82.0199},{"tmdbId":30984,"type":"tv","title":"Bleach","year":"2004","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/5iVUUnE2tgBPypACYNobCKHagfV.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/o0NsbcIvsllg6CJX0FBFY8wWbsn.jpg","rating":8.356,"overview":"For as long as he can remember, Ichigo Kurosaki has been able to see ghosts. But when he meets Rukia, a Soul Reaper who battles evil spirits known as Hollows, he finds his life is changed forever. Now, with a newfound wealth of spiritual energy, Ichigo discovers his true calling: to protect the living and the dead from evil.","popularity":72.2133},{"tmdbId":209867,"type":"tv","title":"Frieren: Beyond Journey's End","year":"2023","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/dqZENchTd7lp5zht7BdlqM7RBhD.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/rBOnrVlck7BIlGeWVlzYiZeg4l2.jpg","rating":8.801,"overview":"After the party of heroes defeated the Demon King, they restored peace to the land and returned to lives of solitude.  Generations pass, and the elven mage Frieren comes face to face with humanity’s mortality. She takes on a new apprentice and promises to fulfill old friends’ dying wishes. Can an elven mind make peace with the nature of life and death? Frieren embarks on her quest to find out.","popularity":73.8421},{"tmdbId":46260,"type":"tv","title":"Naruto","year":"2002","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/xppeysfvDKVx775MFuH8Z9BlpMk.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/5F0HVEgkgP99fEWDjPyikGt9jQi.jpg","rating":8.363,"overview":"Naruto Uzumaki, a mischievous adolescent ninja, struggles as he searches for recognition and dreams of becoming the Hokage, the village's leader and strongest ninja.","popularity":67.504},{"tmdbId":276880,"type":"tv","title":"Please Put Them On, Takamine-san","year":"2025","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/aN4X9QSECSfh5p8S3HtTiWRKJla.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/5AYXcPhbtPe6i1MPnutPhCV6qNd.jpg","rating":7.519,"overview":"Student council president Takane Takamine is a popular star student. On the other hand, Koushi Shirota doesn't have many friends. That all changes when Koushi accidentally discovers Takane's ability to go back in time and alter past actions just by changing her lingerie. After some pestering, Koushi agrees to help Takane and be her closet, by having spare lingerie on hand.","popularity":138.6378},{"tmdbId":94664,"type":"tv","title":"Mushoku Tensei: Jobless Reincarnation","year":"2021","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/gLKOYIMyKlUHW0SVdskhgf9C0yy.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/j9fRIimor0AMFJR9kjZubXcABzZ.jpg","rating":8.6,"overview":"When a 34-year-old underachiever gets run over by a truck, his story doesn't end there. Reincarnated in a new world as an infant, Rudy will seize every opportunity to live the life he's always wanted. Armed with new friends, some freshly acquired magical abilities, and the courage to do the things he's always dreamed of, he's embarking on an epic adventure—with all of his past experience intact!","popularity":63.7293},{"tmdbId":120089,"type":"tv","title":"SPY x FAMILY","year":"2022","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/7NAvPYPAu7MeHwP8E9sn81PqsRh.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/lysUnU6V0VfcthDbviuVlIqgHOR.jpg","rating":8.506,"overview":"A spy, an assassin and a telepath come together to pose as a family, each for their own reasons, while hiding their true identities from each other.","popularity":55.1325},{"tmdbId":46298,"type":"tv","title":"Hunter x Hunter","year":"2011","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/i2EEr2uBvRlAwJ8d8zTG2Y19mIa.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/bFKKyCI89Xq98Gul8cGox8K3sZa.jpg","rating":8.667,"overview":"Gon, a young boy who lives on Whale Island, dreams of becoming a Hunter like his father, who left when Gon was still young.","popularity":54.3571},{"tmdbId":127532,"type":"tv","title":"Solo Leveling","year":"2024","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/geCRueV3ElhRTr0xtJuEWJt6dJ1.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/xMNH87maNLt9n2bMDYeI6db5VFm.jpg","rating":8.665,"overview":"They say whatever doesn’t kill you makes you stronger, but that’s not the case for the world’s weakest hunter Sung Jinwoo. After being brutally slaughtered by monsters in a high-ranking dungeon, Jinwoo came back with the System, a program only he could see, that’s leveling him up in every way. Now, he’s inspired to discover the secrets behind his powers and the dungeon that spawned them.","popularity":52.2632},{"tmdbId":31911,"type":"tv","title":"Fullmetal Alchemist: Brotherhood","year":"2009","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/5ZFUEOULaVml7pQuXxhpR2SmVUw.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/2UG177tWHy7xRmMKWJHB7nAUmKd.jpg","rating":8.71,"overview":"Disregard for alchemy’s laws ripped half of Edward Elric’s limbs from his body and left his brother Alphonse’s soul clinging to a suit of armor. To restore what was lost, the brothers seek the Philosopher’s Stone. Enemies and allies – the corrupt military, the Homunculi, and foreign alchemists – will alter the Elric brothers course, but their purpose will remain unchanged and their bond unbreakable.","popularity":50.2047},{"tmdbId":31910,"type":"tv","title":"Naruto Shippūden","year":"2007","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/kV27j3Nz4d5z8u6mN3EJw9RiLg2.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/z0YhJvomqedHF85bplUJEotkN5l.jpg","rating":8.533,"overview":"After 2 and a half years Naruto finally returns to his village of Konoha, and sets about putting his ambitions to work. It will not be easy though as he has amassed a few more dangerous enemies, in the likes of the shinobi organization; Akatsuki.","popularity":58.3199},{"tmdbId":245842,"type":"tv","title":"Wistoria: Wand and Sword","year":"2024","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/5n0IZQA9MiXn5JBKZibtNhhFSAZ.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/n4VljCX22hbw3RwfxaY8FX8eLzN.jpg","rating":7.9,"overview":"In a world where magic reigns, Will Serfort can’t cast a spell. Though hardworking, Will’s classmates think less of him for it. However, he has a secret strength: his sword. Can Will defy expectations with muscle over magic and blade over wand? Find out in this epic sword-and-sorcery adventure!","popularity":46.0729},{"tmdbId":15226,"type":"tv","title":"C.I.D.","year":"1998","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/3UymnlLfLMKxG8OcFhSnAlnhQfZ.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/1gZrOa2E9DOohEvSLLBJqus2zGu.jpg","rating":5.7,"overview":"A team of dedicated men and women in the Crime Investigation Department will risk everything to solve Mumbai's toughest, most complicated crimes.","popularity":50.6924},{"tmdbId":220542,"type":"tv","title":"The Apothecary Diaries","year":"2023","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/e3ojpANrFnmJCyeBNTinYwyBCIN.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/gffVOVZ2Y9cmVIZ26Gt9ByMGCYH.jpg","rating":8.6,"overview":"Maomao lived a peaceful life with her apothecary father. Until one day, she's sold as a lowly servant to the emperor's palace. But she wasn't meant for a compliant life among royalty. So when imperial heirs fall ill, she decides to step in and find a cure! This catches the eye of Jinshi, a handsome palace official who promotes her. Now, she's making a name for herself solving medical mysteries!","popularity":54.7812},{"tmdbId":37854,"type":"tv","title":"One Piece","year":"1999","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/dB4EDhre2dsC2kxYDavyKWqLQwi.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/2rmK7mnchw9Xr3XdiTFSxTTLXqv.jpg","rating":8.739,"overview":"Years ago, the fearsome Pirate King, Gol D. Roger was executed leaving a huge pile of treasure and the famous "One Piece" behind. Whoever claims the "One Piece" will be named the new King of the Pirates.

Monkey D. Luffy, a boy who consumed a "Devil Fruit," decides to follow in the footsteps of his idol, the pirate Shanks, and find the One Piece. It helps, of course, that his body has the properties of rubber and that he's surrounded by a bevy of skilled fighters and thieves to help him along the way.

Luffy will do anything to get the One Piece and become King of the Pirates!","popularity":45.4891},{"tmdbId":277881,"type":"tv","title":"The Unaware Atelier Meister","year":"2025","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/OPJ7k6DMm1o3A0kIXysgrqVT5w.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/pLWdn8zZcljxHaVGiACNFVrYPMv.jpg","rating":7.182,"overview":"Kurt Rockhans is a kind-hearted errand boy for a hero’s party, the Flaming Dragon Fang. One day, he's banished from the party and finds out he has the lowest rank in combat. In order to make a living, Kurt picks up various jobs and discovers he has astonishing abilities. Though he doesn't realize it yet, Kurt has SSS-rank skills in anything other than fighting, as he sets off on a new journey.","popularity":34.9333},{"tmdbId":72517,"type":"tv","title":"Classroom of the Elite","year":"2017","poster":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185/8BtSk9DGIlS24otIB3qCagVCI6W.jpg","backdrop":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w780/d3yNn379emGP8xztqeOsB9oLNG2.jpg","rating":8.4,"overview":"Kiyotaka Ayanokouji enrolls at the prestigious Tokyo Koudo Ikusei Academy, but is assigned to Class 1-D, where students with behavioral problems are housed. The school awards points equivalent to 100,000 yen per month and allows unusual freedom in classes, masking a more complex system.","popularity":42.655}]}
